views.markdown: If you need help with "Erika", you can contact Paisseon, the developer, via e-mail.
Paisseon is the maintainer of the package "Erika". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "repo.roc4et.de" repo, roc4et.
